{"tid":1285463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我只是需要少許盼望... ...","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:31:20.000Z","uid":254133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1b93b62be732d9b316b5788c365030720e51f86b","tid":1285463,"uid":254133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:50:32.000Z","msg":"香港人！我地就係活生生嘅<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">盼望</span></span></span></strong></strong>！！<br />\n<br />\n呢排香港嘅氣氛係好沉重...好似做咩都冇用<br />\n政府唔理、家人鬧你、港豬話知你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至係幾位朋友付上生命嘅代價 咩都換唔到<br />\n大家都好迷惘...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但係</span></span>，我地仍然係度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請你諗下，難道呢個月唔係我地成世人活得最有意義嘅日子咩？<br />\n最能夠體現香港精神嘅人，唔就係我地咩？<br />\n年輕嘅我地，唔好灰心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地一定比班食人族長命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你有輕生念頭，又咁不幸地睇到我呢段嘢，咁你真係好不幸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為我唔想你死，大家都唔想再有人死</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假如再有人死，只會令香港人更絕望，所以，可唔可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為左香港，唔好死</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段時期係艱難，因此我地更需要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">團結</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢樣嘢想大家做：<br />\n多啲主動搵身邊嘅朋友傾，因為通常有需要嘅人，係唔會主動搵人傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為死左會上天堂，冇人知死左會去邊<br />\n但我肯定<br />\n有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">真&middot;香港人</span></span>嘅地方，嗰度就係天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭要繼續，仲有長命buff，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好放棄</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">7.7見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，我無嘢講"},{"pid":"bae5c7a3b74e8ae7f2abbc2cc894ec33e259f78f","tid":1285463,"uid":254133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:03:31.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家留意下身邊嘅朋友仔<br />\n即使一句鼓勵下 支持下都可以<br />\n唔可以畀香港氣氛繼續沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c7fb849bee136b75fcfb192b2ccb277d7b0841","tid":1285463,"uid":254133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e82d784f80336b2f2904872f50618cfce57ef58a","tid":1285463,"uid":254133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42751077caeb2b7af90d0c55720461284d0ba04","tid":1285463,"uid":254133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a621fb3a0bbbbb704d141bce213f7527d575bd","tid":1285463,"uid":254133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}